# ================================
# GREETINGS
# ================================
# At the very end... show the
# current version and say hello :-)
#
# Briefly show the version number of this starting
# screen session - but only for *one* second:
#  msgwait 1
#  version
# change back to showing messages
# for duration of two seconds:
#  msgwait 2
# this is usually too fast to show messages within workshops.
# it is better to reset it to five seconds for that.
#
# Welcome the user:
#  echo "welcome to screen :-)"
